title: Key Kinahan cartel member arrested after raid in the Netherlands
text: Key Kinahan cartel member arrested after raid in the Netherlands Independent.ie DUTCH police have arrested four men, including a key associate of the Kinahan crime cartel, after an attempted shooting in a pub in the centre of Amsterdam. http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/key-kinahan-cartel-member-arrested-after-raid-in-the-netherlands-35427773.html http://www.independent.ie/incoming/article35427910.ece/524c8/AUTOCROP/h342/Dutchpolice.jpg Dutch police in Amsterdam.
